    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/431224acd997e7b8a59c1624b71aa9aa.avif?t=1709910014\" width=620 height=92 /></span><br>Create your tale in a beautiful world full of adventure and exploration! Tales of Morrow is a semi-survival, adventure, action RPG where you can build on your island, start a farm, travel to other islands riddled with ruins from a past civilization, and fight all enemies who oppose you. Here you will encounter a massive and lively environment with an extensive selection of weapons, tools and plenty to explore. So grab your sword or kick back with a fishing rod under the sunset and begin your story!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore, build, and survive</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/78ac4b9e45ce285fb33f3db2f9486479.poster.avif?t=1709910014\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/78ac4b9e45ce285fb33f3db2f9486479.webm?t=1709910014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/78ac4b9e45ce285fb33f3db2f9486479.mp4?t=1709910014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover ruins and conquer your enemies </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/3972c3ef4489cae5470cb24bbf492f80.poster.avif?t=1709910014\" width=620 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/3972c3ef4489cae5470cb24bbf492f80.webm?t=1709910014\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1783620/extras/3972c3ef4489cae5470cb24bbf492f80.mp4?t=1709910014\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>- Build anything using resources you collect from the islands<br>- Explore procedural islands (No two islands are the same!)<br>- Descend into dark dungeons and ancient cities<br>- Encounter and defeat a wide array of enemies<br>- Grab your pole and angle for countless fish<br>- Start a farm! Scavenge and grow various crops<br>- + much more!<br><br>",
